title: Tiffany Haddish Interview and More
itunes:title: Tiffany Haddish Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had the last black unicorn, Tiffany Haddish stop by, where she spoke about her glow up to fame, haters in the industry, and even gave the guys sex ed 101. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Florida Mayor Teresa Darlene Bradley for using a dead person's handicap sticker for parking. Also, since it is Monday we did our favorite segment "Shoot Your Shot", and lets just say the shooter did a complete air ball.
